elements.title: Emais Roberts
elements.contents: ... that Emais Roberts (pictured) administered the COVID-19 vaccination program in Palau and was one of the first to receive the vaccine in the country?

elements.title: Malagasy secret
elements.contents: ... that millions of people from Madagascar claim ancestral ties to ancient Jews, according to a centuries-old origin myth called the "Malagasy secret"?

elements.title: Kirk Raymond Jones
